people, which will cost 6 billion yuan and provide 5 million
sq.m. of residential housing.
</P>
<P>
The design anticipates an aging society and provides special
consideration for the elderly by providing entertainment and
cultural facilities.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin has more than nine million people and is planning to
make housing a new part of its economic growth. 
