<HEADLINE> SKorean High-Speed Rail Project Faces Possible Suspension </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SEOUL, January 12 (Xinhua) -- Construction of South Korea's
Seoul-Pusan high-speed railway may be suspended as the result of
demands by President-elect Kim Dae-jung's takeover team for a
thorough review of the project.
