Action Party convention on Sunday, Goh, who is the party's
secretary-general, stressed that the market has to be calmed.
Confidence in currencies has to be restored through taking painful
and necessary measures prescribed by the International Monetary
Fund. (Singapore-Goh-Crisis)
</P>
