did not apply for a party ticket. Rao was chargsheeted in several
scam cases including buying MPs and some of the cases are being
tried in the court.
</P>
<P>
It would be wrong if an individual who had laid down certain
principles attempts to throw them to winds when he himself gets
affected, Scindia said.
</P>
<P>
He dismissed suggestions that the entry of Sonia Gandhi, widow
of former Prime Minister Rajiv Gandhi, in active politics had
resulted in a leadership struggle in the Congress. He said that
Sonia's decision to campaign for the party has enthused the rank
and file and she herself has ruled out taking over the reins of
the party.  
