<P>
HONG KONG, January 12 (Xinhua) -- Hang Seng China Enterprises
Index fell 94.51 points to close at 436.51 Monday.
</P>
<P>
The Index, introduced in August 1995, tracks the overall
performance of China's 32 state enterprises listed on the Hong
Kong Stock Exchange.
</P>
<P>
Monday's Hang Seng MidCap 50 Index dropped 146.96 points from
the previous session to close at 889.48.
</P>
