Cambodia in early July 1997 just after Prince Ranaiddh was ousted
from power on charges of negotiating with the Khmer Rouge hard
liners.
</P>
<P>
"I would recommand that the ASEAN nations do not worry
so much about situation in Cambodia," said Hun Sen.
</P>
<P>
"I would welcome them if they are going to give us advice on
economy matters," he added.  
</P>
