<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, January 12 (Xinhua) -- Manila Mayor Alfredo Lim
announced on Monday that he had teamed up with senator Sergio
Osmena for the 1998 presidential elections.
</P>
<P>
Lim, who would run for the presidency, said he and senator
Osmena from the southern Philippines had joined hands in pursuing
their bids in the May 11 elections.
</P>
<P>
