<HEADLINE> Cuba Holds Assembly Elections </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAVANA, January 11 (Xinhua) -- About 83 percent of Cuba's 7.8
million eligible voters took part in the national and provincial
assembly elections Sunday, the National Electoral Commission said.
</P>
<P>
