People's Power and 1,192 representatives for 14 provincial
assemblies.
</P>
<P>
Cuban President Fidel Castro cast his ballot in the eastern
province of Santiago de Cuba, where his name was listed on the
ballot.
</P>
<P>
In a short speech to the people outside the polling station,
Castro said he had voted "as a patriot and a revolutionary."
